    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I've been reading a lot about how it's basically seen as a cornerstone for hitting carbon reduction goals in these cities. From a planning perspective, would you say it's more of an environmental necessity or just another way to manage traffic flow?",
      "source": "evaluator"
